@section Side-by-Side: What You See in Your Terminal
@cindex comparison, thinking vs non-thinking

The table below shows what a user observes at the terminal for each phase
with each model type.

@multitable @columnfractions .20 .38 .42
@headitem Phase @tab Non-thinking (qwen2.5-coder:3b) @tab Thinking (qwen3.5:0.8b)
@item Prefill @tab Spinner: ``Thinking... 230s (prefill)'' @tab Spinner: ``Thinking... 3s (prefill)''
@item First output @tab JSON @code{@{} token appears @tab @code{<think>} prose token appears
